snippet.textDisplay:
The developer of Baten Kaitos...oh this game got my attention back in 2007 I guess!
I thought "this has to be good it's from the company who made Baten Kaitos I & II

Boy it was a game! The graphic was nice, I loved the characters but the story was...well I played it again just to understand  (SPOILER) and I have to say it's a pretty deep and dark story of a little girl who is trapped in an endless spiral of pain and sorrow! Just to live this life over and over again until a yound man entered her world. He's living on the edge of life! A place where he is close to death. After that, the story of that girl changed for the first time and she was able to change her fate.
At the end she was falling in love...a girl who was avoided all the time, who never was loved by anyone because of her illness! I really REALLY love the story! 

It's brilliant in it self! So many hints and you really have to pay attention to it, because it's not so easy to understand! The music is a masterpiece! Well it's from Motoi Sakuraba! He is my favourite VGM composer afterall : )
